01:02:07,040 --> 01:02:08,659
[ Bas akan tiba sebentar lagi. ]

901
01:02:08,660 --> 01:02:09,809
Bas dah sampai.

902
01:02:09,810 --> 01:02:12,765
Naik bas dan turun
selepas sembilan hentian.

903
01:02:13,590 --> 01:02:15,135
Okey. Terima kasih.

904
01:02:18,080 --> 01:02:21,125
Naik bas sekarang.
